embeds.title: Rules
embeds.description:
Hey! Welcome to the Mobile Speedrunning Discord (MSD)! We are a warm and friendly speedrunning community that focuses on playing games on Android and iOS devices. Our chat is normally active and we have a lot of fun together! Having fun does come with rules, and so we expect you'll follow them to the best of your abilities. Failure to abide by the rules can result in a kick or ban.
:no_entry_sign: hate speech.
:no_entry_sign: inappropriate/immature jokes.
:no_entry_sign: shitposting.
:no_entry_sign: spamming.
:no_entry_sign: memes, unless speedrunning related.
:no_entry_sign: swearing occasionally is fine, but don't overdo it.
:no_entry_sign: Discord invites, unless speedrunning related.
:no_entry_sign: NSFW.
:no_entry_sign: phishing.
:warning: English is the main language of the MSD, please stick to speaking English in chat.
